## Self-check

- [ ] Using platform-native font?
- [ ] Honoring safe areas (mobile) / window chrome (desktop)?
- [ ] Touch targets meet platform minimum (44pt iOS / 48dp Android / 24px desktop)?
- [ ] Following platform navigation pattern (tabs / nav / sidebar)?
- [ ] Tested in both light and dark mode?
- [ ] Tested with platform's screen reader (VoiceOver / TalkBack / NVDA)?
